name: Coach Bus Parking School
description:
Coach Bus Parking School!!!
Try to park heavy go nawaz go vehicle!
It is a challenge for you to park a coach in parking space!
Crazy challenging levels and a lot of fun are waiting for you in the city adventure. Driving a party bus in the city adventure is very difficult task. Show your driving skills and park the turbo bus in the parking lot within a limited time.
Features:
• Awesome graphics
• Realistic sound system
• Different buses
• Exciting stages
• Interesting game play
